agent_comment: The issue is clear and actionable, describing a specific problem with manual balancing of channels and proposing a solution in the form of a button for automated balancing. It includes relevant pseudo-code to illustrate the implementation. The request is focused on one well-defined feature and is primarily in English.

The issue describes a specific behavior in the GUI related to the display of decimal values when minting a Taproot Asset, but it is marked as a minor issue and does not provide a concrete, actionable solution or request for implementation. Additionally, it ends with 'just FYI,' which implies it is more of an informational note rather than a clear feature request or bug fix. The focus appears to be vague and does not fully meet the criteria for a 'Good PR.'
